data.description: WELCOME TO 5215 W. HUTCHINSON, A FANTASTIC INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITY OR IDEAL FOR MULTI-GENERATIONAL LIVING. THIS SOLID BRICK 2-FLAT HAS A TOTAL OF 6 BEDS AND 2 BATHS, PROVIDING SPACIOUS AND COMFORTABLE LIVING SPACES. RECENT TUCKPOINTING ADDS TO THE PROPERTY'S DURABILITY AND APPEAL. EACH UNIT FEATURES SEPARATE HEAT, OFFERING INDIVIDUALIZED COMFORT FOR RESIDENTS. THIS GREAT BUILDING ALSO HAS AN UNFINISHED BASEMENT WITH A WASHER/DRYER. THE NEW GARAGE ROOF ENSURES THE SAFETY OF YOUR VEHICLES AND ADDS TO THE PROPERTY'S OVERALL VALUE. SITUATED IN THE HIGHLY SOUGHT-AFTER PORTAGE PARK LOCATION, RESIDENTS WILL ENJOY THE BENEFITS OF A VIBRANT COMMUNITY WITH ACCESS TO PARKS, SCHOOLS, SHOPPING, AND DINING. THE PROPERTY IS MOVE-IN READY, IN A WELL-MAINTAINED CONDITION. THE PROPERTY IS BEING SOLD "AS-IS," PROVIDING AN EXCELLENT CHANCE FOR THE NEW OWNER TO CUSTOMIZE AND MAKE IT THEIR OWN. DON'T MISS OUT ON THIS RARE FIND - SCHEDULE A SHOWING TODAY AND ENVISION THE POSSIBILITIES OF CALLING 5215 W. HUTCHINSON YOUR NEW HOME!
